The Azure TCO Calculator compares on-premises infrastructure costs with Azure cloud costs.

It evaluates:

* Hardware
* Power
* Maintenance
* Staffing
* Licensing

For example, an enterprise can estimate long-term savings from migrating datacenter workloads to Azure.

